children.subject: Has anyone taken CS294-112? Help much appreciated please!

history.content:
How does the workload and difficulty of CS 294-112 compare with undergrad CS classes like CS189/CS170 (which I consider heavy workload and difficult) or CS188(lighter workload and easier)?

Would EE126 + CS294-112 be a heavy workload combination? I have been doing one hard technical(CS170/CS189) + one easy technical(CS186/CS188) for the last two semesters, and I want to have a similar workload next semester if not lighter.

I haven't taken a grad class before. Is it difficult to get help in a grad class? Is the office hours very limited? 

Are most students in CS 294-112 grad students or undergrad?
